    "description": "<strong>Chaotic local couch co-op/pvp warfare madness incoming!</strong><br><br>Be ready to have a great gaming party night with your friend in this 4v4 strategic couch co-op fighting action packed game! Each team has 3 treasure chests that they need to fill with gold coins and protect from the enemy that might try to explode the treasure with a bomb! <br><br>5 minutes round cycling through the current 8 maps available in the game. First team to win 5 round win the game<br><br><strong>PICK A CHARACTER!</strong><br>Pick your favorite character and jump in the warfare!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102680/extras/d5fdd274f1ef3d75ef036522469174d1.poster.avif?t=1771250122\" width=616 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102680/extras/d5fdd274f1ef3d75ef036522469174d1.webm?t=1771250122\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102680/extras/d5fdd274f1ef3d75ef036522469174d1.mp4?t=1771250122\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>FARM GOLD</strong><br>Convert rock into gold at the mining table!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102680/extras/612ed5ae3eb883543f29d4476043128a.poster.avif?t=1771250122\" width=616 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102680/extras/612ed5ae3eb883543f29d4476043128a.webm?t=1771250122\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102680/extras/612ed5ae3eb883543f29d4476043128a.mp4?t=1771250122\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>PUNCH!</strong><br>When you get punched you lose what you currently have in your hand so be careful! Having a sword in your hand increase your punch range and stun the enemy on hit<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102680/extras/e52f5de41803369fb0b0dc263c7132c8.poster.avif?t=1771250122\" width=616 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102680/extras/e52f5de41803369fb0b0dc263c7132c8.webm?t=1771250122\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102680/extras/e52f5de41803369fb0b0dc263c7132c8.mp4?t=1771250122\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>SHOOT!</strong><br>With a gun equipped, you can shoot and stun your target from a distance<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102680/extras/435a6c720c7d7b283a4df3f7fa0da84b.poster.avif?t=1771250122\" width=616 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102680/extras/435a6c720c7d7b283a4df3f7fa0da84b.webm?t=1771250122\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102680/extras/435a6c720c7d7b283a4df3f7fa0da84b.mp4?t=1771250122\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>FILL TREASURE</strong><br>Put the gold in your team treasures and protect them! The first team with a gold coin secured in all their treasure chest win the round<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102680/extras/9908e9de17f3611f9a5316844277b15a.poster.avif?t=1771250122\" width=616 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102680/extras/9908e9de17f3611f9a5316844277b15a.webm?t=1771250122\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102680/extras/9908e9de17f3611f9a5316844277b15a.mp4?t=1771250122\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>DESTROY TREASURE</strong><br>The other way to win a round is by placing a bomb on a treasure chest of the opposing team. If they don't remove the bomb in time they lose the round!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102680/extras/95580beef5adcabd7f87f80d75e562df.poster.avif?t=1771250122\" width=616 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102680/extras/95580beef5adcabd7f87f80d75e562df.webm?t=1771250122\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102680/extras/95580beef5adcabd7f87f80d75e562df.mp4?t=1771250122\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ENVIRONMENT</h2><strong>4 thematics - 8 maps (more on the way!)</strong><br>Every map has a unique configuration that changes the way you play and the strategy available to win the round!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102680/extras/9f45aebccddc063eae1057e2252ead11.avif?t=1771250122\" width=616 height=692 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CHARACTERS</h2><strong>20 playable characters</strong><br>Purely cosmetic but we never know maybe one day they will have their unique abilities or special stats?! Pick your favorite one and jump in the warfare!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102680/extras/5d902e41fb4e36799d9a766e3e24c562.avif?t=1771250122\" width=616 height=347 /></span><br><br><strong>Simple controls : everyone can play! </strong><br>The goal is to have a fun game to play for gaming night with family and friends! Where pro gamer and newbies can have a great time Laughing, yelling and eating their favorite meal together while enjoying a fun co-op/competitive action party game!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >COMPATIBLE WITH &quot;REMOTE PLAY TOGETHER&quot; STEAM FEATURE</h2><strong>(So yes you can do a game online with your friends!)</strong><br>But this is against the purpose of this game! You will miss the opportunity to do an awesome gaming experience so do it at your own risk!<br><br><strong>ARE YOU READY FOR THE COUCH WARFARE?</strong><br>Pick up your controller and call your friend. It's time for a great gaming party!",
